This paper is about weakly supervised semantic segmentation using regularized losses in deep learning. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), as the paper focuses on image segmentation. Other likely sub-categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
